Summary: Took a couple of pics of a contrail, didn't see the white objects.
divs: Sighting DetailsI had just parked and saw a jet contrail so I pulled my camera out to snap a pic. I took two pics from the car with my window down. They are almost identical but the angle is slightly different on the 2nd pic. The two objects show up in both pics. I thought when I saw the 1st pic that the sun had flashed on my lens but the sun wasn't really shining on the lens and the same dots came up on the 2nd pic too. I didn't see the dots when I took the pics.
